{"title":"小朋友②","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":0,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-5092","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>小朋友获得钱以后，就去别人家去熊了=-=，每熊1-3个家需要花费2-4元的费用（别问我是什么费用），只要去熊就要20元的武器费（也是醉了）。现给出小朋友身上有k元。下表有熊家的价格：</p><table width=\"-116\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"\" valign=\"top\" width=\"95\">熊家的个数</td><td style=\"\" valign=\"top\" width=\"95\">1</td><td style=\"\" valign=\"top\" width=\"95\">2</td><td style=\"\" valign=\"top\" width=\"95\">3</td></tr><tr><td style=\"\" valign=\"top\" width=\"95\">价格</td><td style=\"\" valign=\"top\" width=\"95\">2</td><td style=\"\" valign=\"top\" width=\"95\">3</td><td style=\"\" valign=\"top\" width=\"95\">4</td></tr></tbody></table><p>问怎样花钱才能使熊家的个数最多？</p><p>（武器费只要熊家就要，买一次就行）</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>一个数k，代表小朋友有的钱数    </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>输出两个数 m,n,分别代表小朋友花最少钱熊的最多的家的个数，和小朋友花最少钱所剩下的钱数。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一次：25<br></p><p>第二次：40</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一次：3 1</p><p>第二次:15 0</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>熊的家数一定要最多，然后求最少花的钱数，并输出。</p><p>m和n之间要有空格</p><p>20&lt;k&lt;100</p><p><br></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}